{"tid":1787900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭錦滿 ： 理大廚房佬星期五出院","createTime":"2019-12-18T09:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T11:51:43.000Z","uid":22556,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"beec4b52d9d0a60cc8e7f513454db05134b0ba80","tid":1787900,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T09:08:09.000Z","msg":"今日我帶同「理大廚房佬」最愛的山崎麵包銅鑼燒，作最後一次探訪。<br />\n<br />\n外面正在抹黑我熱血公民鄭錦滿，「四眼食人血饅頭」！就此，我表示問心無愧，亦不想再添煩添亂。<br />\n<br />\n「理大廚房佬」與我溝通後，已經將本人姓名從探訪名單上剔除，轉為袁師母陳錦美；他亦已經成功聯絡上張超雄議員、黃毓民、杜汶澤喱騷、國難五金、星火同盟抗爭支援、高登討論區新聞部記者爆炸頭等等朋友，故此我相信他的人身安全能得到保障。<br />\n<br />\n如無意外，本周五他會在朋友陪同下出院，感激醫護人員一直以來的包容及悉心照顧，天佑義民！好人一生平安！<br />\n<br />\n註：此帖圖文經「理大廚房佬」細閱後才公佈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/800421050019891/posts/2704585162936794?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F800421050019891%2Fposts%2F2704585162936794%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2Bur32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=6b69870b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/800421050019891/posts/2704585162936794?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"1f81d90d5be5e57c5b140d9107e21fec4e791171","tid":1787900,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T09:21:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f808debe05fd499cceaa4ea8d6fe35325ecd23df","tid":1787900,"uid":224916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T11:10:00.000Z","msg":"想問出到院後仲有無手尾跟？有無被控？"},{"pid":"23e8317fcd59d1f58178d93e1d4e3c111dee88e5","tid":1787900,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T11:10:49.000Z","msg":"滿囝做到嘢"},{"pid":"1db9a6d3e4f00484ecdf180cbf5e989f2ddabf07","tid":1787900,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T11:13:53.000Z","msg":"廚房佬無事就得"},{"pid":"584d7dbf467db600bba264d6e8f16515423429ce","tid":1787900,"uid":58799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T11:14:23.000Z","